    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 &quot;刺客&quot;礼包</h2><br>“刺客”武器套装里面的物品都能够消灭任何玩家遇到的敌人。世界上最强大的武器和独特自动手枪在一起可以帮你成为优秀战士！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/47aa506a282c33f97199455959ec0ac7.poster.avif?t=1728127139\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/47aa506a282c33f97199455959ec0ac7.webm?t=1728127139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/47aa506a282c33f97199455959ec0ac7.mp4?t=1728127139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>套装中有两把武器：合适任何职业（除了SED）的手枪，和“步枪手”职业自动抢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/aa2f0779887253ea3d62fca777fa4671.poster.avif?t=1728127139\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/aa2f0779887253ea3d62fca777fa4671.webm?t=1728127139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/aa2f0779887253ea3d62fca777fa4671.mp4?t=1728127139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Glock 18</h2>Glock 18C 是一款全自动手枪，位于底部的拉杆式快慢机可以使它进行全自动射击，很合适PVE战斗。该枪是其他版本的改型，应奥地利反恐单位的要求而开发。此外武器具有33子弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/37af0d63c79d5ae375aa13b16ec0a95b.avif?t=1728127139\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >АК-47</h2>这是最早在苏联由米哈伊尔·卡拉什尼科夫开发，是一款配备快慢机的导气式突击步枪。这款枪也被称为卡拉什尼科夫、或者在俄语里被称为卡拉什。这种枪具有低成本、耐久性好和易操作的特点，即使面世已有六十多年，这种型号及其各种改型依然是世界上使用最为广泛的突击步枪。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/e5dd1c78ad132584819a39b401d5d76f.avif?t=1728127139\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700710/extras/65c3bace5e4458ce4e037aca38d12770.avif?t=1728127139\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。",
